snippet.title: Solo Leveling - Gameplay Trailer - NTP - PC & Mobile - KR
snippet.description:
Netmarble just announced their new game lineup in the Netmarble Together with the Press (NTP) event in South Korea. This one seems to be a new Action-RPG game based in the Korean Manhwa "Solo Leveling", the game will be available on PC and mobile. This game is still in development, no release date yet. 

BGM: Jay Ray - Cold Light feat. Jimmie Strimell
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ldJW68rL-4s
